<p>It seems to be the season&#8230; Migration Season, that is! So many new Macs, so many migrations, so much data, and so many questions! Thankfully your two favorite geeks have answers, as does the MGG Family. Press play and listen as John and Dave take you through all these and more. Of course, there&#039;s more: Quick Tips are aplenty and there might even be some Cool Stuff Found! Whatever it is, you&#039;ll enjoy learning at least five new things this episode!&nbsp;</p>
